Package weka.classifiers.collective.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Clock
    A little helper class for clocking and outputting times.
    CollectiveHelper
    Contains various useful methods, e.g., for writing to a file.
    CollectiveInstances
    A helper class for initializing labels and flipping class labels.
    CollectiveLog
    Used to output some internal statistics for a Collective Classifier.
    ConfidentFlipper
    Flips a label only if the previous and the current prediction differ more than a given percentage.
    FlipHistory
    A flipping algorithm, that flips the label only if the previous and the current (possibly new) label disagree more than a certain percentage.
    Flipper
    Abstract class for algorithms that flip labels according to a certain function.
    RankedInstance
    This class is used for storing the distributions generated by the different trees per instance.
    RankedInstanceComparator
    A comparator for the RankedInstance class.
    RankedList
    This class resembles a simple sorted array of Instance's with their according distributions.
